{"tid":1761813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂！人地免費幫手搞黃色經濟圈仲未有人Share出去？","createTime":"2019-11-29T07:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T05:06:11.000Z","uid":33595,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"8e467146c6690471af2b786c6952af13cb816e84","tid":1761813,"uid":33595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://bit.ly/35Bzwv0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35Bzwv0&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=09a1d36c\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/35Bzwv0</a><br />\n<br />\n人地公司整合咗出面D黃店地圖你地都冇人幫手推，咁冇人性<br />\n之前人地講明左唔洗錢幫手同D黃店宣傳，你班粉皮得咁少人留言幫手update資料，仲話做大個黃色經濟圈，淨係顧住自己食<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GoodsAndNice.HK/photos/a.1663959150510034/2414382295467712/?type=3&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGoodsAndNice.HK%2Fphotos%2Fa.1663959150510034%2F2414382295467712%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26__tn__%3D-R&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=1afbfb02\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GoodsAndNice.HK/photos/a.1663959150510034/2414382295467712/?type=3&amp;__tn__=-R</a><br />\n<br />\n人地仲話除左食店個D都可以搵佢地做廣告啊，你地推曬身邊D黃色店出去比人未啊？<br />\n你推少一間就少一間有人知，你地係咪想黃店手足蝕到入肉先黎呻冇幫手宣傳啊<br />\n<br />\n唔該全世界同我入黎推爆佢，拎曬D資料同我去派街坊，推黃店資料出街洗版啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xvTVDZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xvTVDZ.jpg&h=8bd034fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36f7731ddc01ed475932c8e89c0d2ca4a8f4b6cb","tid":1761813,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:14:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1c3de80105110900adee85ad3610ea94583bf725","tid":1761813,"uid":306381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:16:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1536fac4c748193bba083e16a71732d7b708450b","tid":1761813,"uid":33595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29