\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FThankYouPresidentTrump&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=8fb2342c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ThankYouPresidentTrump</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港 #美國 #自治 #HKAA #trump #LiberateHK #驅逐共黨<br />\n#天滅中共 #ThankYouUSA #ThankYouTrump #已出不反"},{"pid":"0f6c1bbe4d4dc1f60eb4a8edfe63c324b9444bda","tid":1761813,"uid":165127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7bb94dba037e255dffc0360e32f1caa0997705c8","tid":1761813,"uid":33595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d1d9db7694d3309faa82092e195e0b1dd22a8e96","tid":1761813,"uid":238543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人整藍店地圖？見到有人幫親藍店真係想嘔，成班冇腦。"},{"pid":"8c640d9928ad08b144774f33dd4e5823dc957572","tid":1761813,"uid":32596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:07:04.000Z","msg":"開心SHARE"},{"pid":"636c355fdff3a7aa228db77d9956f44abfa18314","tid":1761813,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"推左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52082a3f7a727d0e8287990087f57a2f6749d1f","tid":1761813,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd71cb3da9e6e6dfa187196c6fecf9bbbfed3da","tid":1761813,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1d9db7694d3309faa82092e195e0b1dd22a8e96","tid":1761813,"uid":238543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人整藍店地圖？見到有人幫親藍店真係想嘔，成班冇腦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:21:12.000Z","msg":"食左黃店等於藍店少一份錢<br />\n無謂一定又變成捉鬼"},{"pid":"a482fa222eb7a149f2e62d3aa72ca695cbc589c7","tid":1761813,"uid":192824,"like":0,"di